message: Wrong lexicographical order for 'ai.idylnlp.opennlp.custom.EncryptedDataOutputStream' import. Should be before 'java.util.zip.GZIPOutputStream'.
'}' at column 5 should be on the same line as the next part of a multi-block statement (one that directly contains multiple blocks: if/else-if/else, do/while or try/catch/finally).
Abbreviation in name 'writeUTF' must contain no more than '2' consecutive capital letters.
